	<element name="Ability Score Improvement" type="Class Feature" source="KH" id="ID_KH_CLASS_FEATURE_KEYBADE_WIELDER_ABILITY_SCORE_IMPROVEMENT_KEYBLADE_WIELDER">
		<compendium display="false" />
		<description>
			<p>When you reach 4th level, and again at 6th, 8th, 12th, 14th, 16th, and 19th level, you can increase one ability score of your choice by 2, or you can increase two ability scores of your choice by 1. As normal, you can't increase an ability score above 20 using this feature.</p>
		</description>
		<sheet display="false" />
		<rules>
			<select type="Class Feature" name="Improvement Option (Keyblade Wielder 4)" supports="Improvement Option,Keyblade Wielder,4" level="4" />
			<select type="Class Feature" name="Improvement Option (Keyblade Wielder 6)" supports="Improvement Option,Keyblade Wielder,6" level="6" />
			<select type="Class Feature" name="Improvement Option (Keyblade Wielder 8)" supports="Improvement Option,Keyblade Wielder,8" level="8" />
