	<element name="Socket" type="Class Feature" source="KH" id="ID_KH_CLASS_FEATURE_KEYBLADE_WIELDER_SOCKET">
		<description>
			<p>At 10th level you have gained some of the Moogle's knowledge and can now add a socket to any item, this allows you alter the original item by attaching a Keychain. Only one Keychain can be equipped to each item at a time.</p>
		</description>
		<sheet>
			<description>You may add a socket to an item at the cost of 1 day plus 1000 gold.</description>
		</sheet>
	</element>
	
